    <briefdescription>
<para>Helper to detect if a type is a function pointer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a type trait used for compile-time type detection. It allows templates to behave differently based on whether a type is a function pointer or not.</para>
<para>The primary template returns false for all non-function-pointer types. Specializations can be added to return true for specific function pointer types.</para>
<para>@SINCE_2_5.11</para>
<para>Example usage: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">template</highlight><highlight class="normal">&lt;</highlight><highlight class="keyword">typename</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>T&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">IsFunctionPointer&lt;void<sp/>(*)(T*)&gt;<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">static</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">const</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">bool</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="structDali_1_1IsFunctionPointer_1a211764eea950a1bbb90067a8b327bcf3" kindref="member">value</ref><sp/>=<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">true</highlight><highlight class="normal">;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>True<sp/>for<sp/>function<sp/>pointers</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Usage:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">IsFunctionPointer&lt;void<sp/>(*)(</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal">*)&gt;<ref refid="structDali_1_1IsFunctionPointer_1a211764eea950a1bbb90067a8b327bcf3" kindref="member">::value</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>true</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structDali_1_1IsFunctionPointer_1a211764eea950a1bbb90067a8b327bcf3" kindref="member">IsFunctionPointer&lt;CustomDeleter&gt;::value</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>false</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
